original_title: I Go To The Rock: The Gospel Music of Whitney Houston
overview: The unmistakable voice of Whitney Houston is powerful and timeless. She reached the pinnacle of pop success becoming one of the most accomplished recording artists of all time. But her heart was always in Gospel music, and it profoundly influenced her life and career.  From her first performance in front of an audience to her best-selling Gospel album of all time, The Preacher's Wife, experience how profoundly Gospel music influenced her personal life and helped shape her career. Join host CeCe Winans and discover Whitneyâ€™s deep faith and love of Gospel music.
title: I Go To The Rock: The Gospel Music of Whitney Houston
